# The granite embedding model is NOT tracked in git (the ~107MB ONNX file exceeds GitHub's
# 100MB-per-file limit). It lives under public/models/granite/ locally and is either
# downloaded from HuggingFace by `npm run fetch-model` or built with
# scripts/quantize-granite.py. The prebuild SHA-256-verifies whatever is on disk.
